---
import Section from "./Section.astro";
---
<section id="home" aria-labelledby="hero-heading" class="relative bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-xl px-4 py-24 lg:grid lg:grid-cols-12 lg:items-center lg:gap-12">
      
      <!-- Text Content -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-6 text-center lg:text-left" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Organization">
        <h1 id="hero-heading" class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-gray-900">
          <span class="text-indigo-600">Laravel™</span> Impossible? Let’s see.
        </h1>
  
        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-700">
          <a href="https://laravelcompany.com" 
             title="Official Laravel Agency & Employee-Owned Company" 
             class="text-blue-600 hover:underline" 
             rel="noopener noreferrer">
             Laravel™ Agency
          </a> 
          <strong>is a 100% employee-owned ESOP company</strong> since 2004. We advance Laravel™ through research, systems engineering, and global collaboration while delivering powerful solutions combining technical excellence with strategic design.
        </p>
  
        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-700">
          Our team of 100+ Laravel experts builds future-proof 
          <span class="font-semibold text-green-600">ESOP software solutions</span> 
          for global innovators including <strong>BMW</strong>, <strong>Amazon</strong>, and <strong>Samsung</strong>. 
          We specialize in creating platforms that empower employee ownership models through cutting-edge technology.
        </p>
  
        <p class="text-base text-gray-600">
          As both practitioners and advocates of employee ownership, we code with purpose, people, and performance in mind — whether developing 
          <em>Employee Stock Ownership Plans</em> or building systems for <em>Worker Cooperatives</em>.
        </p>
  
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 italic" itemprop="description">
          Founded in Romania in 2004, we're a global, remote-first Laravel agency with 100+ developers working on ESOP-related software solutions since 2020.
        </p>
  
        <div class="mt-8 flex justify-center lg:justify-start gap-4">
          <a href="#contact" 
             class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-indigo-600 px-6 py-3 text-white text-sm font-medium hover:bg-indigo-700 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-indigo-300 dark:focus:ring-indigo-800 transition">
            Contact Us
          </a>
        
        </div>
      </div>
  
      <!-- Visual Content -->
      <div class="mt-10 lg:mt-0 lg:col-span-5 motion-safe:animate-fadeInUp">
        <img 
          src="logo-light.svg" 
          alt="Laravel™ Agency Logo" 
          class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg  transition-transform duration-500 hover:scale-105" 
          width="500" height="300" 
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
  
    </div>
  </section>
  